{"id": "a1e09e5a-d876-4624-96fd-a4ff1061baf1", "task_id": "be46c162-6a9b-48ca-8637-f9266090ec0a", "path": "templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>NEO-KYOTO LOGIN // SYSTEM</title>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400..900&family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #00ffff; /* Neon blue */\n            --secondary-color: #ff00ff; /* Neon pink */\n            --background-dark: #1a0f2b; /* Dark purple-ish background */\n            --text-color: #e0e0e0;\n            --border-glow: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            --shadow-glow: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.4);\n            --error-color: #ff3333;\n        }\n\n        *, *::before, *::after {\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-dark);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden; /* Prevent scrollbar from glitch effects */\n            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(30, 0, 50, 0.8) 0%, rgba(10, 0, 20, 1) 100%);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Glitch effect background */\n        body::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(0deg, transparent 24%, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 25%, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 26%, transparent 27%, transparent 74%, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.1) 75%, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.1) 76%, transparent 77%);\n            background-size: 100% 2px;\n            animation: scanline 8s linear infinite;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            opacity: 0.1;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scanline {\n            0% { background-position: 0% 0%; }\n            100% { background-position: 0% 100%; }\n        }\n\n        .login-box {\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--shadow-glow), 0 0 30px var(--shadow-glow) inset;\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            animation: flicker 1.5s infinite alternate;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes flicker {\n            0%, 19.9%, 22%, 24.9%, 26%, 27.9%, 30%, 32.9%, 34%, 35.9%, 38%, 40%, 42%, 44%, 46%, 48%, 50%, 52%, 54%, 56%, 58%, 60%, 62%, 64%, 66%, 68%, 70%, 72%, 74%, 76%, 78%, 80%, 82%, 84%, 86%, 88%, 90%, 92%, 94%, 96%, 98%, 100% {\n                text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--primary-color);\n            }\n            20%, 21%, 25%, 25.5%, 28%, 29%, 33%, 33.5%, 36%, 37%, 41%, 41.5%, 45%, 45.5%, 49%, 49.5%, 53%, 53.5%, 57%, 57.5%, 61%, 61.5%, 65%, 65.5%, 69%, 69.5%, 73%, 73.5%, 77%, 77.5%, 81%, 81.5%, 85%, 85.5%, 89%, 89.5%, 93%, 93.5%, 97%, 97.5% {\n                text-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--primary-color), 0 0 20px var(--primary-color), 0 0 30px var(--secondary-color);\n            }\n        }\n\n\n        .input-group {\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--secondary-color);\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"],\n        input[type=\"password\"] {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);\n            outline: none;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        input[type=\"password\"]:focus {\n            border-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--secondary-color), 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.4);\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        /* Autofill styles for better theme integration */\n        input:-webkit-autofill,\n        input:-webkit-autofill:hover,\n        input:-webkit-autofill:focus,\n        input:-webkit-autofill:active {\n            -webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 0px 1000px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) inset !important;\n            -webkit-text-fill-color: var(--text-color) !important;\n            border-color: var(--primary-color) !important;\n        }\n\n\n        .glitch-button {\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            background: transparent;\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            cursor: pointer;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);\n            outline: none;\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button::before,\n        .glitch-button::after {\n            content: attr(data-text);\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: transparent;\n            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);\n            opacity: 0; /* Hidden by default */\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease; /* Smooth fade in/out */\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button::before {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            left: 2px;\n            text-shadow: -1px 0 var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button::after {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            left: -2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 0 var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button:hover::before {\n            opacity: 0.7; /* Show on hover */\n            animation: glitch-anim-1 1.5s infinite alternate-reverse; /* Start animation on hover */\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button:hover::after {\n            opacity: 0.7; /* Show on hover */\n            animation: glitch-anim-2 1.5s infinite alternate-reverse; /* Start animation on hover */\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button:hover {\n            background-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary-color), 0 0 40px var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .glitch-button:active {\n            transform: translateY(2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-anim-1 {\n            0% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n            10% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 30%, 0 30%); transform: translate(-2px, -2px); } /* Slice 1 */\n            20% { clip-path: polygon(0 70%, 100% 70%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); transform: translate(2px, 2px); } /* Slice 2 */\n            30% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 10%, 0 10%); transform: translate(-1px, 1px); } /* Slice 3 */\n            40% { clip-path: polygon(0 90%, 100% 90%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); transform: translate(1px, -1px); } /* Slice 4 */\n            50% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n            60% { clip-path: polygon(0 20%, 100% 20%, 100% 40%, 0 40%); transform: translate(-3px, 0); } /* Slice 5 */\n            70% { clip-path: polygon(0 60%, 100% 60%, 100% 80%, 0 80%); transform: translate(3px, 0); } /* Slice 6 */\n            80% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n            90% { clip-path: polygon(0 40%, 100% 40%, 100% 60%, 0 60%); transform: translate(0, -2px); } /* Slice 7 */\n            100% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-anim-2 {\n            0% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n            15% { clip-path: polygon(0 10%, 100% 10%, 100% 40%, 0 40%); transform: translate(1px, 1px); } /* Slice 1 */\n            25% { clip-path: polygon(0 60%, 100% 60%, 100% 90%, 0 90%); transform: translate(-1px, -1px); } /* Slice 2 */\n            35% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 20%, 0 20%); transform: translate(2px, 0px); } /* Slice 3 */\n            45% { clip-path: polygon(0 80%, 100% 80%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); transform: translate(-2px, 0px); } /* Slice 4 */\n            55% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n            65% { clip-path: polygon(0 30%, 100% 30%, 100% 50%, 0 50%); transform: translate(0, 2px); } /* Slice 5 */\n            75% { clip-path: polygon(0 50%, 100% 50%, 100% 70%, 0 70%); transform: translate(0, -2px); } /* Slice 6 */\n            85% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n            95% { clip-path: polygon(0 10%, 100% 10%, 100% 30%, 0 30%); transform: translate(1px, 1px); } /* Slice 7 */\n            100% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); } /* Base */\n        }\n\n        .links {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .links a {\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 0.8em;\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n            letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .links a::before,\n        .links a::after {\n            content: attr(data-text);\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: transparent;\n            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);\n            opacity: 0; /* Hidden by default */\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease; /* Smooth fade in/out */\n        }\n\n        .links a::before {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            left: 1px;\n            text-shadow: -1px 0 var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .links a::after {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            left: -1px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 0 var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .links a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color); /* Change base text color on hover */\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary-color), 0 0 20px var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .links a:hover::before {\n            opacity: 0.7; /* Show on hover */\n            animation: glitch-link-1 0.8s infinite alternate-reverse linear;\n        }\n\n        .links a:hover::after {\n            opacity: 0.7; /* Show on hover */\n            animation: glitch-link-2 0.8s infinite alternate-reverse linear;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-link-1 {\n            0% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); }\n            20% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 20%, 0 20%); transform: translate(-1px, 1px); }\n            40% { clip-path: polygon(0 80%, 100% 80%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); transform: translate(1px, -1px); }\n            60% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 10%, 0 10%); transform: translate(-0.5px, 0.5px); }\n            80% { clip-path: polygon(0 90%, 100% 90%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); transform: translate(0.5px, -0.5px); }\n            100% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-link-2 {\n            0% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); }\n            15% { clip-path: polygon(0 10%, 100% 10%, 100% 30%, 0 30%); transform: translate(1px, 0); }\n            35% { clip-path: polygon(0 70%, 100% 70%, 100% 90%, 0 90%); transform: translate(-1px, 0); }\n            55% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 20%, 0 20%); transform: translate(0.5px, -0.5px); }\n            75% { clip-path: polygon(0 80%, 100% 80%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); transform: translate(-0.5px, 0.5px); }\n            100% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); transform: translate(0, 0); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"login-box\">\n        <h1>NEO-KYOTO LOGIN //</h1>\n        <form id=\"loginForm\" action=\"/login\" method=\"POST\">\n            <div class=\"input-group\">\n                <label for=\"username\">USERNAME:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" required autocomplete=\"username\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"input-group\">\n                <label for=\"password\">PASSWORD:</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" required autocomplete=\"current-password\">\n            </div>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"glitch-button\" data-text=\"LOGIN\">LOGIN</button>\n        </form>\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"glitch\" data-text=\"FORGOT PASSWORD?\">FORGOT PASSWORD?</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"glitch\" data-text=\"REGISTER NEW ACCOUNT\">REGISTER NEW ACCOUNT</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const loginForm = document.getElementById('loginForm');\n\n            loginForm.addEventListener('submit', (event) => {\n                // IMPORTANT: As per requirements, NOT using event.preventDefault() blocking actual form submission.\n                // The form will submit naturally to the /login endpoint via POST.\n                console.log('Login form submitted naturally.');\n                console.log('Username:', loginForm.username.value);\n                console.log('Password:', loginForm.password.value);\n\n                // Client-side validation could be added here, but it should not block form submission.\n                // For example, display an error message if fields are empty, but still allow the form\n                // to proceed, letting the backend handle the ultimate validation and response.\n                // The 'required' attribute on inputs provides basic browser-level validation without JS.\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "This `index.html` file creates a cyberpunk-themed login page using standard HTML5, CSS3, and Vanilla JavaScript. The page features a dark, futuristic aesthetic with neon accents and glitch effects.\n\n**HTML Structure:**\n-   A `div.login-box` acts as the main container for the login form, centered on the page.\n-   It includes a `<h1>` title with a flickering animation.\n-   The login `form` uses `action=\"/login\"` and `method=\"POST\"` to ensure a standard HTML form submission, as required. It contains input fields for username and password with appropriate labels and `autocomplete` attributes.\n-   A `button` styled with a glitch effect is used for submission.\n-   Additional `<a>` links for 'Forgot Password' and 'Register' also feature hover glitch effects.\n\n**CSS Styling:**\n-   Global styles set a dark background, a futuristic font (`Orbitron`), and a pixelated font (`Press Start 2P`) for headings and labels.\n-   CSS variables (`:root`) are used for consistent neon colors and shades.\n-   The `.login-box` has a semi-transparent dark background, neon borders, and glow effects.\n-   `h1` includes a `flicker` animation for a classic neon sign effect.\n-   Input fields are styled to be semi-transparent with glowing borders that change on focus.\n-   Critical glitch effects for the submit button and links are implemented using `::before` and `::after` pseudo-elements with `clip-path` animations. These animations are triggered specifically on `:hover` to provide interactive visual feedback.\n-   A subtle `scanline` background animation adds to the cyberpunk atmosphere.\n\n**Vanilla JavaScript:**\n-   A `DOMContentLoaded` listener ensures the script runs after the page is fully loaded.\n-   An `eventListener` is attached to the login form for the `submit` event.\n-   **Crucially, `event.preventDefault()` is explicitly NOT used**, allowing the form to perform its default submission action to the `/login` endpoint. The JavaScript merely logs the form submission details to the console, demonstrating basic client-side interaction without interfering with the backend's expected form handling.", "dependencies": []}, "created_at": "2026-05-17 14:52:40.790717"}